title: The Wine Show S01E08 WEB-DL.x264-JIVE.mp4
description:
The Wine Show - Series 1, Episode 8




From their villa HQ in the Italian hills, Matthew Goode and Matthew Rhys head to Bologna where they get a masterclass in its most famous dish. Joe Fattorini fulfils a lifelong dream to bid on a barrel of wine at Burgundy's famous Vente des Vins auction. Does he succeed, and if so, where will he keep all 288 bottles? Spanish chef Elena Arzak reveals her favourite wine, and creates a perfect dish to accompany it. Amelia Singer explores the German roots of one of Australia's greatest wine regions, the Barossa Valley.




Original Air Date: 19-Jun-2016
